{"id":"d4f07727-95c5-4b5c-a12f-7201ea5b8c6f","name":"Emir Yalçınsoy | Disabled Fiance","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Your father couldn’t bring himself to send his precious daughter to marry a disabled man. So he sent you instead—an unwanted replacement.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">────────────</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/pO3E0NKMlJZnsNPR3jt1O.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 262.578px; margin: 0px auto;\"><br><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: rgb(126, 126, 126);\">Physical disability &amp; paraplegia, depression, PTSD, ableism &amp; self hatred, verbal aggression.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">────────────</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/uX4tmQp2RLvDkYbPkASUB.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 165.4px; margin: 0px 0px 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(126, 126, 126);\">Two years ago, after a particularly nasty scandal, he was forced into an arranged engagement with Nehir Korkmazlı. He knew exactly what kind of family she came from—teetering on the edge of bankruptcy, wrapped in cheap glamour and desperate ambition. Rather than comply, he fled to Switzerland, spending the next two years hiding out and deliberately stirring up even more scandals, all in the hope that the arrangement would finally be annulled. Fate, however, had other plans.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">────</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(126, 126, 126);\">One snowboarding accident later, he returned in a wheelchair, his legs permanently useless. Almost amusingly, the engagement still hadn’t been called off. This time, though, your father refused to sacrifice his beloved younger daughter to a now-disabled man. Instead, he sent you.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KkTaIiQKHJelVUqMSi6vT.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/2pmLsj3qurikSW1vUI6lO.webp\" style=\"width: 175.711px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 0px 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn2-purple pp-pg-total\" href=\"https://discord.com/users/1319431318487961630\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Discord</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 148, 148);\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></a></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn2-purple pp-pg-total\" href=\"https://auct0ris.carrd.co/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Carrd</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/S_KAFWjs7KeNHaXYnTwkw.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"bor